                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18170416-84-victim676 t18170416-84-viclabel435"></join>. On the 11th of March, between three and four o'clock, I missed my shoes-the prisoner was my <rs id="t18170416-84-deflabel436" type="occupation">servant</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18170416-84-defend675 t18170416-84-deflabel436"></join>. I placed an officer outside the door; when the prisoner went out in the evening, he stopped him with the shoes.</p>
               <p>
            
